Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:56.79,HiguDef,,0,0,0,,{\be1}"Maybe it's because I've started to lose some hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:56.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽入）“最近 髪の毛が\N少なくなってきたせいか―”
